When you try to do something, you try to remedy something, you're blinding yourself to what's naturally already here. You go into a subdivision. But if you continue to allow the dullness, like you are, allow that to be within your knowingness, your natural knowingness, which at first is like the sun hiding behind the mountains, this awareness, then it starts to rise in our experiences in our lives, and it's quite prominent. Not a single iota of your experience is not exposed by the rays of awareness or clear light. Everything will always be in this.

It gets stronger and stronger. You have to trust me on this. Ten years ago, if someone told me this, I'd be in the same boat, wondering if it gets more powerful. You don't do anything. Let the sun rise naturally on your dullness. Trust that the sun's rising.

If anything gets into your dullness, it will be this, because there's an invigoration on a cellular level, on the space level, on the bindu level. It's even more nano than particles. This is how your cells get invigorated through awareness practice. I'm not saying it's the ultimate elixir, but it can help with healing.

Remember, it's like a pot of water. Frozen or boiling, dull or elated, the pot of awareness holds the water the same. Stir a whirlpool, the pot sits there, especially if it's a good pot. The pot is stable, like space, familiar, the wholeness, empty cognition, the womb for any creation, any abiding, and any cessation. Very familiar to us.

